For those stuck at 99%:

Type this in notepad to make the new cue file. 

FILE "ims-ck.bin" BINARY
  TRACK 01 MODE1/2352
    INDEX 01 00:00:00

Rename the file with a .cue extension. After which everything should function correctly. 

Or:

Mount the bin on the new version of Daemon Tools.
